                            <comment id="12771603" author="lancenorskog" created="Thu, 29 Oct 2009 20:50:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Please add tests or add to the existing example dih config files.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12771743" author="noble.paul" created="Fri, 30 Oct 2009 02:36:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is a 1.5 issue. It will be committed later sometime. BTW you are welcome to contribute tests &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
